    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As of Jackson 1.6, you can use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>JsonNode node = mapper.valueToTree(map);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>JsonNode node = mapper.convertValue(object, JsonNode.class);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Source: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6967583/jackson-is-there-a-way-to-serialize-pojos-directly-to-treemodel\">is there a way to serialize pojo's directly to treemodel?</a></p>\n"
  } ],
