  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11828368/convert-java-object-to-jsonnode-in-jackson",
  "closed_reason" : "Duplicate",
  "title" : "Convert Java Object to JsonNode in Jackson",
  "body" : "<p>Is it possible to directly convert a Java Object to an JsonNode-Object?</p>\n\n<p>The only way I found to solve this is to convert the Java Object to String and then to JsonNode:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper(); \nString json = mapper.writeValueAsString(object);\nJsonNode jsonNode = mapper.readTree(json);\n</code></pre>\n"
}